<br>
I guess the point of my little 2cp post here is that &quot;role-play extremist&quot; do not have a leg to stand on since you really can't regulate the &quot;correct&quot; way to role-play.  But a &quot;name extremist&quot; does have a leg to stand on becuase there ARE rules to lean on. <p><BR>
